  "description": "A breathtaking aerial view of a turquoise coastline. The water transitions from crystal clear near the rocky shore to a deeper, vibrant blue as it extends towards the horizon. A narrow strip of beach is visible, backed by rocky cliffs and distant, hazy mountains. The foreground is dominated by a pebble beach with clear water lapping against the stones, revealing underwater rocks and the seabed. The sky is a clear, bright blue, contributing to the overall sense of serenity and natural beauty.",
